data.description: Beautiful, well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in gated community with playground for kids!  This floor plan offers beautiful kitchen custom cabinets,,  stainless steel appliances, tile flooring and pantry and has open floorplan to living area. Large Living room for entertaining with hardwood flooring &  fireplace. Lg Master bedroom with trey ceilings, and large walk in closet. Master bath has double vanities,  , garden tub, shower and private toilet. 2   Additional bedrooms  and full bath.  Large Screened back  porch with built out deck, gazebo, inlaid stone fire pit area for entertaining with a great view of the  prettiest sunsets!   HOUSTON County Taxes!
